data.description: Welcome to this charming country farmhouse nestled in the heart of Pinewood Estates, Sour Lake! This home offers over 3,400 sq ft of comfortable living space on a sprawling .77-acre lot. Inside, you'll discover 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a tastefully updated interior, where the old-world charm seamlessly blends with modern comforts. The spacious 5th room can effortlessly serve as a bedroom or transform into a bonus room for hobbies, thanks to its versatility. This home is zoned for Hardin Jefferson ISD allowing highly sought educational opportunities for loved ones. Explore the backyard with a private basketball court, perfect for friendly games & entertainment with neighbors. Experience the serene country lifestyle while enjoying modern comforts and ample space for your needs. The seller is planning to replace the floors prior to closing.  A sample tile is in the home for review.  Don't miss the chance to make this Pinewood Estates gem your forever home. Schedule a viewing today!
